    <div class="book2">
        <div class="book-title"><b>Name:</b> Pizza Margherita</div>
        <div class="book-auth"><b>Cuisine:</b> Italian</div>
        <div class="book-pub"><b>Popularity:</b>★★★★★</div>
        <div class="book-pri"><b>Price:</b>$8 - $20 per pizza</div>
        <div class="book-exp"><b>Overview:</b>Pizza Margherita is a classic Neapolitan pizza named after Queen Margherita of Savoy. It features a simple yet flavorful combination of fresh tomatoes, mozzarella cheese, fresh basil, salt, and olive oil, representing the colors of the Italian flag. The dough is traditionally hand-tossed and baked in a wood-fired oven.</div>
